prune_images.description: Deletes images not attached to any template.

user.description: Deletes a user with the given user_id.

compute.description: Deletes a compute from the controller with the given compute_id.

project.description: Deletes a project with the given project_id.

template.description: Deletes a template with the given template_id.

image.description: Deletes an image with the given image_id.

acl.description: Delete an ACL entry with the given ace_id.

role.description: Deletes a role with the given role_id.

group.description: Deletes a user group with the given user_group_id.

pool.description: Deletes a resource pool with the given resource_pool_id.

pool_resource.description: Deletes a resource pool with the given resource_pool_id and resource_id.

link.description: Deletes a link between two projects with the given project_id and link_id.

node.description: Deletes a node from a project with the given project_id and node_id.

drawing.description: Deletes a drawing from a project with the given project_id and drawing_id.

role_priv.description: Removes a privilege from a role with the given role_id and privilege_id.

user_from_group.description: Remove a user from a user group with the given user_id and group_id.

snapshot.description: Deletes a snapshot from a project with the given project_id and snapshot_id.
